function is also called as named method /generalization of code
  the  function  have global scope
  in that function process it is local scope
  eg:-
          a,b  are perameters
  def add(a,b):----->global scope
    res=a+b ----->local scope
    print(res)
    return res
tup=add(10,10)----->arguments
print(tup)


